title: Best Remaining Free Agents, Game of Thrones Recap (Football 5/7)
description:
Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough are here to give Will Brinson some much deserved time off. The guys chat the possibility of the overtime rules being changed, the Bears; kicking woes, best remaining free agents and possible landing spots and recap this week's episode of Game of Thrones. 
*Episode recorded before Bears traded for kicker Eddy Pineiro.
